clickhouse_sql.name: A
clickhouse_sql.query:
SELECT 
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name') AS service_name,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'git_commit') AS git_commit,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'goarch') AS go_arch,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'goos') AS go_os,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'goversion') AS go_version,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'telemetry_sdk_name') AS telemetry_sdk_name,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'telemetry_sdk_version') AS telemetry_sdk_version
    -- JSONExtractString(labels, 'version') AS version
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'keda_build_info';

widgets.description: shows current replicas against max ones based on time difference
widgets.title: Current/max replicas (time based)

widgets.description: shows current replicas against max ones

clickhouse_sql.name: A
clickhouse_sql.query:
SELECT
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'namespace') AS namespace,
    JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s_hpa_name') AS k8s_hpa_name,
    (max(value) - min(value)) AS delta_replicas
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'k8s_hpa_current_replicas'
  AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'namespace') = '$namespace'
  AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'k8s_hpa_name') = concat('keda-hpa-', '$scaledobject_name')
  AND unix_milli >= (now() - INTERVAL 1 MINUTE)
GROUP BY namespace, k8s_hpa_name;
